Class WaitCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • bour.camus.gameofgooses.models.cells.AbstractCell
      • bour.camus.gameofgooses.models.cells.WaitCell
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICell

    public class WaitCell
extends AbstractCell
    WaitCell represents a type of cell where the Player has to wait a specific amount of time before being able to play again.
    Author:
    Armand BOUR, Tristan CAMUS
